node.text:
2019 has been a magical year and we all have many things to be thankful for, however there are many things we need to be better at in 2020. 
Climate change is happening right before our eyes, we all need to understand that we need to do positive changes to the way we live... we are running out of time. 
Something else that is really close to my heart is how we treat one another. I see a society moving backwards and becoming a more dangerous place for many of us. 
We need to learn to embrace our differences and treat each other with love and kindness. 💓

These are my wishes and hopes for the new year.

May you have a wonderful time with your loved ones and may the new year bring you health, love, and everything your heart desires!! ❤️😘
Xx
Donatella
